---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — AmirHossein Movahedi", seo={{
	title: "About AmirHossein Movahedi",
	description: "Learn about my background, interests in complex systems and neuroscience."
	}}>
	<main class="page">
		<!-- About Section -->
		<section class="card">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h2>👤 About Me</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="card-content">
				<p>
					I was born on March 31, 2002, in Isfahan—often referred to as the 
					"Half of the World"—one of Iran's largest and most historically significant cities.
				</p>
				<h3>Passions & Hobbies</h3>
				<p>
					Beyond academics, I'm passionate about card games, which have deepened my understanding of probability theory and strategic thinking. Games serve as a bridge between theoretical mathematics and practical decision-making.
				</p>
				<h3>More</h3>
				<p>
					I'm driven by curiosity about how complex systems work, from neural networks to financial markets. The intersection of mathematics, physics, biology, and artificial intelligence fascinates me,
					and I am committed to contributing meaningful research in these areas.
				</p>
				<p>
					Beyond my current research, I am deeply interested in the nature of human cognition, particularly perception, creativity, and scientific reasoning. One question that continually motivates me is whether it is possible
					to design computational systems capable of genuine creativity—not merely generating outputs from existing patterns, but formulating new scientific theories, discovering fundamental principles, or creating original works
					of art in ways that resemble human thought. This question lies at the intersection of neuroscience, cognitive science, and artificial intelligence and represents one of the long-term directions I hope to explore. 
					The ideas discussed in ("LLM Can't Jump") capture many of the questions that inspire my research.
				</p>
			</div>
			</div>
		


			<div class="interests-grid">
				<h3>🧠 Research Interests</h3>

				<div class="interest-item">
					<h3>Brain Modeling and Computational Neuroscience</h3>
					<p>Computational models of the human brain and neural dynamics.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="interest-item">
					<h3>Time Series Analysis</h3>
					<p>Exploring temporal patterns and predictive modeling in complex datasets.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="interest-item">
					<h3>Probability Theory</h3>
					<p>Deep dive into the mathematical foundations of uncertainty and probabilistic reasoning.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<!-- Skills Section -->
		<section class="card">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h2>💻 Technical Skills</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="skills-container">
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-name">Python</div>
					<div class="skill-levels">
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-name">R</div>
					<div class="skill-levels">
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

				<div class="skills-container">
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-name">Latex</div>
					<div class="skill-levels">
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-name">Matlab</div>
					<div class="skill-levels">
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
				<div class="skills-container">
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-name">C+</div>
					<div class="skill-levels">
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
						<span class="level inactive"></span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-name">Linux</div>
					<div class="skill-levels">
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
						<span class="level active"></span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>




		</section>


	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		padding: 60px 6vw 120px;
		display: grid;
		gap: 60px;
	}
	/* Card Sections */
	.card {
		background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		padding: 48px;
		border-radius: 24px;
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border 0.25s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		border: 1px solid  rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);;
		box-shadow:
			0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35),
			0 0 30px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.15);
	}

	.card-header {
		margin-bottom: 32px;
		padding-bottom: 16px;
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
	}

	.card h2 {
		font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 1.9rem);
		margin: 0;
		color:  #ffffff;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.card-content {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
	}

	.card-content p {
		margin: 0 0 20px;
	}

	.card-content p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
	.interests-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(600px, 1fr));
		gap: 24px;
	}

	.interest-item {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11, 229, 245, 0.08), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08));
		border: 1px solid rgba(11, 124, 245, 0.2);
		padding: 24px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		transition: all 0.25s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	/* .interest-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: -100%;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15), transparent);
		transition: left 0.6s ease;
	} */

	/* .interest-item:hover {
		border-color:  #f59e0b;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12));
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
	} */
/* 
	.interest-item:hover::before {
		left: 100%;
	} */

	.interest-item h3 {
		font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.interest-item p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* Skills Section */
	.skills-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 32px;
	}

	.skill-item {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 10px;
	}

	.skill-name {
		font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color:  #ffffff;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.skill-levels {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.level {
		width: 32px;
		height: 32px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
		cursor: pointer;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.level.active {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2562c4 0%, #0d2463 100%);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
	}

	.level.inactive {
		background: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.2);
		border-color: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
	}

	.level:hover.active {
		transform: scale(1.1);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
	}

	.level:hover.inactive {
		border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
		background: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
	}

	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.card {
			padding: 36px;
		}

		.education-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page {
			padding: 40px 6vw 80px;
			gap: 40px;
		}

		.hero-section {
			padding: 60px 0;
		}

		.hero-section h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.card {
			padding: 24px;
		}

		.card-header {
			margin-bottom: 24px;
		}

		.interests-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.card,
		.education-item,
		.education-item::before,
		.interest-item,
		.interest-item::before {
			transition: none;
			transform: none;
		}
	}
</style>